{
  "stem": "27285.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, of course, Laura organized the children, and then she organized the place for-- in Prague for me to come back to to study or whatever.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I make it short, because it was a nice time and OK.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Anyway, it was-- it was a very Christian gentleman who-- his name is Psemisl Pitel-- who took care of all those children.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Not necessarily only Jewish children, because he was a humanist and he wanted every children to have a better time or whatever.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But it was also very funny, in a way, because he was very religious.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he tried to explain to us what death meant.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Death for-- for us who went through a lot of different kind of death, we couldn't even-- I mean, I couldn't relate to it somehow.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It's-- I found it absurd, really absurd even then.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Because I remember, for instance, he told us that death is like you go from one room to the other and leave your coat behind, and that's it.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I said to myself-- I was then still very quiet and I couldn't speak to the person who was so completely nothing our kind of life to tell him that death meant a lot of things, but definitely not leaving a coat behind.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So that was only one little example how difficult it was for somebody to comprehend who wasn't there or hasn't been near it.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Also, he was really a very, very good person.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "He even brought milk to children to Terezin, and I don't know what different kind of dangers.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "He was arrested when in Germany, and he was arrested from the Czech communist.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He was always arrest-- he was really a fantastic person.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
